description: Demolition of the existing buildings on site and erection of a building fronting Holloway Road rising from five storeys to seven storeys and containing commercial units on ground floor and residential units above. Erection of a second building to the rear of no 54 Holloway Road rising from five to six storeys, comprising residential units, a total of 119 units are proposed.
decision_conditions: The development hereby permitted shall begin not later than three years from the date of this decision.
